# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share this in the project.
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if used with a virtualenv, it might be ignored.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock contains exact versions.
#   Depending on the project type, you may or may not want to commit it.
#poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock contains exact versions.
#pdm.lock

